        <item>
            <title>苦主怒斥 HKExpress 讲大话 + 网民撑追究　香港快运称得到乘客同意才调位</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/16/hkexpress-2/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hkexpress-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/16/hkexpress-2/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 12:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1250707</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">早前，有网民在 Facebook 专页「HK Express 香港快运及旅行资讯关注组」发文，称搭乘香港快运航班 UO690 时，目击一名家长带同两名中学生子女要求已付费选位的乘客让座。事后，香港快运出声明指因机型转换，需按规定为未成年乘客调位，但事主其后回应，质疑香港快运，为何不让未成年乘客与其父母对调。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250717 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-9-694x163.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="163" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-9-694x163.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-9.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250718 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451412023_1016006278-2-488x580.jpg" alt="" width="488" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451412023_1016006278-2-488x580.jpg 488w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451412023_1016006278-2.jpg 757w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 488px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网民在 Facebook 专页「HK Express 香港快运及旅行资讯关注组」发文（图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/638762621229829/posts/1032254121880675/">HK Express 香港快运及旅行资讯关注组</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">事件发生后，香港快运回复明报查询表示「根据规定，当中两位未成年的乘客不能坐在紧急出口座位排，因此与相关家庭解释调位需要、并得到另一排四位乘客的同意后（当中包括两位已付费自选座位的乘客），迅速安排对调。香港快运已向协助对调的乘客解释并承诺会退回自选座位的费用。如乘客未符合相关安全规定，香港快运会为该乘客重新安排替代座位。」0&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;.</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250720 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/untitled2-2-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/untitled2-2-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/untitled2-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲香港快运回复明报查询表示，需按规定为未成年乘客调位（图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/638762621229829/posts/1032254121880675/">HK Express 香港快运及旅行资讯关注组</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">事主在群组隔空回应，指「由头到尾我哋冇人协商过」、「check-in 𠮶阵时系一样嘅座位号码，去到 Boarding 𠮶阵时被通知拦截转位！」。更质疑香港快运「如果照 UO 所讲，未成年人不能坐在逃生座位，但是他们的父母是成年人，为什么父母不能坐在两个逃生座位，而是硬性换了我们的座位！」，事主强调会追究到底。有网民支持事主的举动，并批评香港快运「无耻」、「讲大话」、「一 D 都唔识尊重人」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250714 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-8-694x554.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="554" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-8-694x554.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-8.jpg 1128w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲事主回应指「由头到尾我哋冇人协商过」并会追究到底，获网民支持</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250723 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-10-694x512.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="512" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-10-694x512.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-10.jpg 1220w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲批评香港快运「无耻」、「讲大话」、「一 D 都唔识尊重人」（图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/638762621229829/posts/1032254121880675/">HK Express 香港快运及旅行资讯关注组</a>）</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/638762621229829/posts/1032254121880675/">HK Express 香港快运及旅行资讯关注组</a>、<a href="https://finance.mingpao.com/fin/instantf/20240716/1721101471627/%e5%82%b3%e6%80%aa%e7%8d%b8%e5%ae%b6%e9%95%b7%e6%8c%be%e5%ad%90%e5%a5%b3%e6%90%b6%e5%ba%a7%e4%bd%8d-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%bf%ab%e9%81%8b%e8%a7%a3%e7%95%ab-%e5%9b%a0%e6%a9%9f%e5%9e%8b%e8%bd%89%e6%8f%9b-%e6%8c%89%e8%a6%8f%e5%ae%9a%e7%82%ba%e6%9c%aa%e6%88%90%e5%b9%b4%e4%b9%98%e5%ae%a2%e8%aa%bf%e4%bd%8d">明报</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/16/hkexpress-2/life-tech/travel/">苦主怒斥 HKExpress 讲大话 + 网民撑追究　香港快运称得到乘客同意才调位</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
